citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:00 p.m. on 16
November 2021.
Upon arrival at the facility, contact was made with the licensee's daughter. The licensee and facility representative were
not home and were unavailable for inspection.
End Section
